Description:
	This folder contains all mechanical parts of the project
	The electrical framework box has been realized in 3mm aluminium

Files:
	DR350_rally.dxf                           The electrical framework box for Suzuki DR350 motorbyke with TwalCom motorcycle
	                                          front fairing.
	Koso_instrumentation_attachment.dxf       The small part used to connect the Koso instrumentation
